{"tid":1921671,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「半山手足」警方拘捕7名男子　涉1月遮打花園集會襲擊警員","createTime":"2020-03-12T06:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T08:09:11.000Z","uid":75778,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b0cf98db433c147d406a8ed588a68c6124d61267","tid":1921671,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:16:14.000Z","msg":"警方拘捕7名男子　涉1月遮打花園集會襲擊警員<br />\n<br />\n有團體在1月19日發起在中環遮打花園集會，集會進行大約兩小時，警方指因現場出現暴力情況，要求終止集會，及後有警員受到襲擊。毒品調查科警司鄒旺忠說，有人用雨遮、伸縮棍及磚頭施襲，4名警員受不同程度傷害，包括頭部有裂傷要聯針、手指骨骨折，以及頭骨破裂要接受手術移走磚頭碎塊。鄒旺忠說，警方翻查大量片段後鎖定疑犯，昨日在<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港島半山區、</span></span> 黃大仙、藍田及將軍澳，以有意圖傷人及非法集結罪，拘捕7名年齡介乎13至34的本地男子。<br />\n<br />\n2020-03-12 12:28:10<br />\n<br />\nwe connect! 有錢人都可以好有良心<br />\n仲要行埋出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57905a414538997e8b79b50137505d16eab03ab8","tid":1921671,"uid":173844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:02:06.000Z","msg":"死黑警拉完又再屈打成招 用酷刑迫供<br />\n法官繼續當睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d7f765f267fd029b847f5807c33184c78fc723","tid":1921671,"uid":167567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:03:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab855abcb7788c15ab4abfe530847c4e5c9eb2f","tid":1921671,"uid":135011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:04:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2eb1c486b43d4d051c5cf862de863e12ed55269","tid":1921671,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T07:04:57.000Z","msg":"亂捉的"},{"pid":"80c6df7f4120df3773c4c3cd31dc3a82144ee8a8","tid":1921671